{"tid":234377,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【滅亡危機】霍金再次警告：人類須於100年內離開地球","createTime":"2017-05-08T09:07:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-08T10:38:53.000Z","uid":45926,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"456c248a7d7f022259e4f4fd1b6945bb62af8720","tid":234377,"uid":45926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T09:07:15.000Z","msg":"來源：TechStart<br />\n<a href=\"http://techstart.presslogic.com/2017/05/08/article/25009/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftechstart.presslogic.com%2F2017%2F05%2F08%2Farticle%2F25009%2F&d=%2BrTTj2V4oNsvrkryR3gjd8P%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=648c287a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://techstart.presslogic.com/2017/05/08/article/25009/</a><br />\n近日著名物理學家霍金表示，人類必須於未來100年內離開地球，否則會有滅亡的危機，所有人都應該作好準備，明白到其他星球生活的急切性。<br />\n<br />\nViral Thread<br />\nPhoto by Viral Thread<br />\n霍金曾在去年一次演說中表示，人類只能在地球存活1000年，核戰、全球暖化、基因改造病毒，以及人工智能都是人類需要面對的重大威脅。早前霍金參與即將播出的 BBC 紀錄片 Expedition New Earth 時，再次發出警告，他表示人類在地球上的生活僅餘100年，氣候變化、小行星撞地球，以及人口急速增長，都是導致人類滅亡的潛在原因。<br />\n<br />\nSecond Nexus<br />\nPhoto by Second Nexus<br />\n不到一年時間，霍金預計人類在地球生活的年限，由1000年大幅減至100年，可見他對人類的前景並不感到樂觀。<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：Viral Thread、CNBC"},{"pid":"5094b6bb091ca1d841f9483b7abe311c2a667259","tid":234377,"uid":102841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T09:08:57.000Z","msg":"理撚得你宇宙大爆炸，我要返工！！！"},{"pid":"71b353631a538965212f4dfde36b68d529c7bc61","tid":234377,"uid":30972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T09:09:33.000Z","msg":"風水佬呃你十年八年 霍金就......."},{"pid":"1ac8aaa49e745c9127d9a5ff0e5d1247dc0b1810","tid":234377,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T09:12:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>風水佬呃你十年八年 霍金就.......</blockquote><br />\n本來諗住呃一千年 依家一百年算ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cd822e5b2ca94c58e8389beb25e46b30965f2a5","tid":234377,"uid":45926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl